{"tid":867603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遏止中美洲移民 川普威脅關閉美墨邊界","createTime":"2018-10-18T21:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T00:45:39.000Z","uid":41818,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"43c18c865b56445de70d2a14687cb7b65e635f65","tid":867603,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T21:49:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1053013864244219904?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1053013864244219904%3Fs%3D09&d=USo9LOJMBp8EuMlQhn0d7zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8b04ee64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1053013864244219904%3Fs%3D09&h=a7dbee66\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1053013864244219904?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普今天揚言，如果墨西哥無法遏止中美洲移民「進犯」，他將派兵關閉美墨邊界。<br />\n<br />\n在美國期中選舉投票不到3週的時間之際，川普領軍的共和黨人正在奮戰以保有國會的多數黨地位；現在也是數以千計的宏都拉斯民眾向北前進，穿越瓜地馬拉邁向美國的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n在此關頭，川普發出一連串推文展開攻擊，責怪反對黨民主黨。<br />\n<br />\n川普發推文說：「我目睹瓜地馬拉、宏都拉斯和薩爾瓦多侵犯我們的國家，這些國家的領導人沒有採取行動遏止大批的移民，移民當中包括許多罪犯在內，而民主黨就是帶頭的人（因為他們要「開放邊界」和現有軟弱的法律）。」<br />\n<br />\n他指出：「除了停止支付所有款項給這些國家（他們似乎無力管控自己的人民）之外，我必須要求墨西哥遏止移民進犯，如果無法做到，我將徵調軍隊並且關閉我們南方的邊界！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2yKrXDr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yKrXDr&d=USo9LOJMBp8EuMlQhn0d7zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=369c2012\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2yKrXDr</a>"},{"pid":"a75db1e9d00265ce48835f9978482372328c2f2a","tid":867603,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T21:58:56.000Z","msg":"Trump threatens to call US military to close southern border as 4,000-strong migrant caravan pushes north<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/us/trump-threatens-to-call-us-military-to-close-southern-border-as-4000-strong-migrant-caravan-pushes-north\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Ftrump-threatens-to-call-us-military-to-close-southern-border-as-4000-strong-migrant-caravan-pushes-north&d=USo9LOJMBp8EuMlQhn0d7zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=12cf3017\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Ftrump-threatens-to-call-us-military-to-close-southern-border-as-4000-strong-migrant-caravan-pushes-north&h=50d1e7e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/us/trump-threatens-to-call-us-military-to-close-southern-border-as-4000-strong-migrant-caravan-pushes-north</a>"},{"pid":"630f281957e977fe14766035385d8c035d8ea5ed","tid":867603,"uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:03:09.000Z","msg":"「移民」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗審批自己黎ge叫移民，唔叫非法入境者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09703e3de545a980f2e54ef8ba46412a66e2ef48","tid":867603,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:06:41.000Z","msg":"偷渡"},{"pid":"303063c1e84c7d83ca9214091cd8113ee83364e3","tid":867603,"uid":997,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"630f281957e977fe14766035385d8c035d8ea5ed","tid":867603,"uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T22:03:09.000Z","msg":"「移民」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗審批自己黎ge叫移民，唔叫非法入境者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T23:28:54.000Z","msg":"地球太多左膠<br />\n要起個集中營清洗班左膠先得"},{"pid":"079a39a7809450b8ab2